schools.name: Ray D Corbett J High School

data.description: *Seller is offering $5,000 towards closing cost*. STOP THE CAR!!! If you're looking for a 5-bedroom home, on a corner lot, with a big yard, in a newer neighborhood and in a prestigious school district in Schertz/Selma...Then LOOK NO FURTHER! Why wait months to move into a home, when you can move into your dream home right away! This home was built in 2017 and still looks like new. Primary bedroom is conveniently located on the first floor and the primary bath features double vanity, separate soaking tub, separate shower, and a walk-in closet. The kitchen features granite countertops, beautiful cabinets, a gas stove and an island that opens up to the main living area. Dining room is located at the front of the home and could also be used as an additional living room or office space/study. Upstairs features 4 bedrooms and a large game room/loft! The big backyard and front yard feature an automatic in-ground sprinkler system. Backyard also features a covered patio and privacy fence. Neighborhood amenities include a basketball court, playground, sports court and community park! Home is in the prestigious SCUCISD, a short distance from Rose Garden Elementary School and Corbett Middle School! Located 5 miles from Randolph Air Force Base, 11 miles from BAMC, 20 miles from Ft. Sam Houston and 8 miles from The Forum. Easy access to HWY I10, FM 78 and I-35. Close to lots of shopping and entertainment.
